title: Walking distance to the UofM St. Paul Campus! In-Unit W/D 1Bed/1Bath
posting_body: ['Modern Living Greenway Village Natural Elements Bring A Comfortable, Down-to-Earth FeeI', 'To This One Bedroom!!', "The open chef's kitchen, efficient as it is beautiful, featuring custom Maplewood cabinetry and a large island with quartz countertops that include an overhang for barstools seating.", 'Enjoy a four-burner Fisher Paykel oven range and grill top and two rack oven.', 'The kitchen also has a built-in Miele dishwasher.', 'Plus, Fisher Paykel refrigerator and freezer with a hidden Ice cube storage for your next cool drink.', 'Situated on the other side of the chef’s Kitchen are one..two..three bedrooms.', 'The one..two..three bedrooms are spacious, elegant, warm allowing for a queen-sized bed or seating area and more..', 'There is a massive walk-in closet and secondary closets that line one full wall for you all to enjoy.', 'Central air conditioning recessed lighting and pull shades.', 'Plus, a laundry room with stacked Fisher Paykel washers & dryers.', 'We are conveniently located near the University of Minnesota Minneapolis & and St. Paul campuses and the University of St. Thomas.', '<URL>', '<URL>', '1570 Eustis St.', 'Lauderdale, MN']
